graph TD
    subgraph Device ["User's Device (Browser + OPFS)"]
        SQLite["SQLite Database<br/>(JSON-LD nodes + metadata)"]
        IndexedDB["IndexedDB<br/>(CRDT State)"]
        Commits["Versioning Commits (Log)<br/>(Content-addressed)"]
        
        SQLite ---|"One node = one row"| SQLite
        SQLite ---|"Checksum per row"| SQLite
        
        IndexedDB ---|"Yjs document encoded"| IndexedDB
        IndexedDB ---|"Write-ahead log"| IndexedDB
        
        Commits ---|"Immutable / Parent chaining"| Commits
    end
